hymns.lyrics:
Verse 1
A dahte hong pai un, na vul na pan un,
Hehpih tokhom mai ah hong khuk din’ un;
Na lung liam na, nat na hong pai hong gen un;
Vantung’ dam sak lah dah na om lo hi.

Verse 2
Lungsim hawmte’ nuamna, lam khialte’ khuavak,
Vul ngei lo, mual ngei lo, lawpna hong lak,
Kha Siangtho Huhpa in hong nem hi nuam tak;
“Vantung’ dam sak lah dah na om lo hi.”

Verse 3
En un, Hin’na Anlum en un, Hin’na tui,
Pasian’ tokhom mai pan hong luang suk tui;
Hong pai un, hih lai ah itna pawi kilui;
Vantung’ dam sak lah dah na om lo hi.

Verse 1
Ci damin nipi khat sung, Pasian in hong kem lai a,
Tu ni in Ama inn sung, Thupha sang ding i ngak ta;
Ni sagih sung nuam bel hi, Vantung tawl damna lim hi.
Ni sagih sung nuam bel hi, Vantung tawl damna lim hi.

Verse 2
Mawh phelna ding hehpihna, Hong Tanpa’ min in kong ngen;
Hong mu sak in Na maipha Mawhna zumna bei ta hen;
Tu ni lung khamna bei in, Nang sung hong tawldam sak in.
Tu ni lung khamna bei in, Nang sung hong tawldam sak in.

Verse 3
Na min kong phat laitak un, Nong nai na hong phawk sak in;
Na mai kong kilak lai un, Na vanglian hong mu sak in;
Ko ngah ding vantung nuamna, Hong ciam khol sak in, Topa.
Ko ngah ding vantung nuamna, Hong ciam khol sak in, Topa.

Verse 4
Nangma lungdam na thu in Mi sia puah, mi pha hehnem;
Na thupha’n ta tam tawi in, Siatna khempeuh a pha’n lem;
Tua bang piang hen, Nipi teng, Vantung Pawlpi tun’ mateng.
Tua bang piang hen, Nipi teng, Vantung Pawlpi tun’ mateng.

Verse 1
Gal dona awng un, Gal nai zo, en un! Topa’ dial khai un Sang tak in;
Gal dal silh in la, Kip tak ding in la, Lai Siangtho hilhna, Na sik san in.

Sakkik:
Khai leh! ding un, dial kiim hong kikhawm un;
Lim tak, ki ging! na kihilh sawn un, Kuan un, mai nawt,
Hawsiana ki ko un; Khazih in makaih hi galkap hon.

Verse 2
Eima lam mah in Zo ding thei khol in Gal te ngap thawh in I kuan hi;
I lum leh i dial Ni ah te zial zial; Thumaan in thukhual lel ngei lo hi.

Verse 3
Mi khempeuh’ Pasian, Hehpihna hong pia’n, Ko a neu a lian Hong huh in;
Gal zawh ciang in ah Nangma mai tang ah Hong suak nung zawh na Lukhu khu in.

Verse 1
Kei Topa a hing ei ve, Tu’n zong leitung ah om;
A hin’kik ke’n thei gi ge, Mite’n bang gen ta leh;
Amah’n hong hehpih thei a, Hong hopihna ka za;
Amah ka sap laitak in hong nai gi ge.

Sakkik:
Hing e, hing e, hong hon Khazih Topa,
Hong tonpih a, hong hopih hi, Ka pai na khempeuh ah;
Hing e, hing e, mihing hon khia Topa;
Bang ka ci theih hiam, nong cih leh, Ka lung sungah hing hi.

Verse 2
Ka kiim leitung mun khempeuh Ah hong itna ka mu,
Lungkham na ka thuak zel hang, Ka lungkia ngei kei ding;
Huihpi nun’na teng ah Amah’n hong kha ke’n ka thei;
Amah hong kilat ding ni hong tung ding hi.

Verse 3
Nuam un, nuam un, Zeisu mi, Lungdam in la sa un;
Hin’ tawntung Haleluiah Zeisu Khazih Kumpi
Muan’na tawh a zong mite’n Amah mu thei ding uh,
Tua bang itna a nei midang om ngei kei.

Verse 1
Hong Honpa kiang ah hong pai meng in,
Lai Siangtho ah lam hong lah bang in;
Eite laizang ah tu ni’n ding in;
“Hong pai ve,” ci’n hong sam.

Sakkik:
Mawhna khialnate siangtho nung ah,
Topa mai ah kikhop ciang in ah,
Tawntung inn nuam vantung khua sungah,
Nuam pha mahmah ding hi.

Verse 2
Ngai sin! “Naute hong pai veuvua” ci;
I vekpi in kipaak in diang ni,
Eite in Amah va teel tawm ni;
Zekai ke’n, pai ni, tu’n.

Verse 3
Ngaihsun pha in, tu ni’n hiah om lai;
Hong thu piakna pha limtak in ngai!
Mi gi mahmah tu’n zong hong sam lai;
“Nong pai nai uh hia,” ci.

Verse 1
Hong it zaw ning, Topa Hong it zaw ning;
Khuk din’ a kong thumna Nang hong ngai ding.
Hih bang hi kong thumna; Khazih hong it zaw ning,
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning.

Verse 2
Ni dang leitung nopna Ka lung gulh pen;
Tu in kong deih Nangmah, A hoih pha pen.
Tu in kong deih Nangmah, Khazih hong it zaw ning,
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning.

Verse 3
Dah na nat na thuak hang, Phamawh sa lo;
Nangma sawltak te bang La ka sa zo;
Ka sa khawm amau bang; Khazih hong it zaw ning,
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning.

Verse 4
Ka sih laitak in ah Nang kong phat ding;
Ka hu tawpna in ah Ka vaikhak ding;
Ka ngen lailai hihmah; Khazih hong it zaw ning
Hong it zaw ning, Hong it zaw ning.

Verse 1
Hong pai san ke’n, migi Topa Kong thum hong ngai in;
Mi dangte kiang na baan’ bangmah, Kei hong kheng kei in.

Sakkik:
Topa, Topa, Kong thum hong ngai in;
Mi dangte kiang na baan’ bangmah, Kei hong kheng kei in.

Verse 2
Hehpihna Na tokhom mai-ah, Kisik kong khukdin;
Nang hong huh in ka up lah na; Noptuam hong pia in.

Verse 3
Nangma phatna bek ka suang hi, Na mai muh-na ding;
Na thupha tawh Nong phel ding hi, Lung zan dam na ding.

Verse 4
Ka nuamna teng bulpi Nangmah, Hin’ na sang pha zaw;
Leitung vantung om lo kuamah, Nang sang a pha zaw.

Verse 1
Lungdam thu zeel sak un, mi omna ci teng ah,
Mihing lungsim omna, mihing gal tamna ah;
Tapidaw leii khempeuh lungdam thu gen sak un;
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!

Sakkik:
Huhpa hong pai khin ta! Huhpa hong pai khin ta!
Vantung Kha Siantho pen, Pa’n piak ding hong ciam pen;
Lungdam thu zeel sak un, Mi omna ci teng ah;
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!

Verse 2
Zan hun saupi bei ta, zing khua hong vaak zo ta;
Lungsim vangik pi teng, heh na hu ging veng ta,
Ni taang kham mual pan in, hong suah khiat tak ciang in;
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!

Verse 3
A kha sung zatui tawh, kumpi te’ To hat pa’n
Thongkia kha khempeuh tung hong puak, hotkhiat kicing;
Thong pi hawm sung tengah, zawh na la pi hong ging;
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!

Verse 4
Gen zawh loh itna siang! ka leii in bang ci in
Gen zawh loh hehpihna, mi vak vai tung gen ding
Amah leh A meel taang, sungah ka om theih na’ng
Huhpa hong pai khin ta!

Verse 1
Itna siangtho Itna, ki cing, Vantung nuamna, hong tuak suk;
Nong hehpihna lung khup na ding Ko sung hong lam in Na Buk.
Zeisu aw, hehpihna Na dim, Itna Siang kicing Na hi;
Lawp a liing ko khempeuh lungsim Hotna tawh Nong veh ding hi.

Verse 2
Lung hi mawh mi lungsim sung ah Itna Nangma Kha guan’ in;
Kote khempeuh Nangma sung ah Tawldam na hong luahsak in.
Ko mawh nopna lungsim pai khia’n Alpha le Omega in,
Upna pan a cingsak Pasian, Ko lungsim hong khah khia in.

Verse 3
Hong pai in a hon zo pen Pa, Nang nuntak na hong guan’ in;
Na inn ah hong tum meng in la Pai khia nawn peuhmah kei in.
Thupha kong piapia ding uh a, Na’na ka sem ding uh hi;
Na itna sung ah kipakta Tawlnga lo kong phat ding hi.

Verse 1
Kha Siangtho meivak na tawh, Keima lungsim sung taang aw;
Khuamialna na hawl khia in, Khuamial na khuavak sak in.

Verse 2
Kha Siangtho vangliat na tawh, Kei lungsim na sawp siang aw;
Khialhna in a sawt veipi, Ka lung sung ah uk zo hi.

Verse 3
Kha siangtho lungdam na tawh, Ka lungsim sung nuamsak aw;
Gim na khempeuh hawl khia in, Dah na lungsim damsak in.

Verse 4
Kha Siangtho a dik mi aw, Ka lungsim sung ah om aw;
Milim khempeuh susia in, Nangmah guak bek na maang in.

Verse 1
Khazih galkap te’n ah Gal sim ding kuan un;
Eite mai a masa Zeisu mitsuan un;
Khazih eite Mangpa, Makai hi lo maw;
En un, A’ dial pai na Gal phual lam ma nawh!

Sakkik:
Zeisu galkap te’n ah Gal kap ding kuan un;
Singlamteh pua un la, Na mai lam nawt un.

Verse 2
Zeisu min a zak ciang Dawi mite tai uh;
Nawt un, tua a hih ciang Na mualsuah dong uh;
Phatna aw kizak ciang Dawi gam kiling hi;
Lawmte, tua ahih ciang, Awngun phatna pi.

Verse 3
Galkap honpi bang in Pawlpi’n masot hi;
Tang mi siangte bang in I tot na khat hi;
Eite kikhen lo in Pum khat bek i hi;
Lawp le zuih kikhat in Hong ki it sak hi.

Verse 4
Kumpi za sia thei hi; Kumpi gam kip kei;
Hih hang Zeisu’ Pawlpi Cikmah’n sia thei kei;
Dawi in Pasian’ Pawlpi Cik ciang zo ngei kei,
Khazih hong ciamsa hi A ciam peel ngei kei.

Verse 5
Tua hi a hong pawm un Mi khempeuh in ah;
Ko tawh hong sa khawm un Gal zawh nuam na la;
A minthang pahtawi un Leitung vantung ah
Tatsat lo in phat un Khazih Kumpipa.

Verse 1
Han thuk sung ah lum hi, Kei Honpa Zeisu;
A ni tun’ding ngak hi, Kei To Zei su’n.

Sakkik:
Han sung pan hong tho to zo,
Vanglianpi tawh gal te zo gawp zo;
Khuamial gam pan Gal zo in hong tho to hi,
A mi siang te maan’ pih ding hing kik zo hi;
Hing kik zo, hing kik zo,
Halleluiah Hing kik zo.

Verse 2
Cin’ hang in mawk na hi, Hong Hon Zeisu’ han;
Ciam teh hang mawk na hi, Kei To Zei su’n.

Verse 3
Sihna’n len zo lo hi, Hong Honpa Zeisu;
Dal na te su gawp hi, Kei To Zei su’n.

Verse 1
Lai Siangtho, Pasian thu bu,
Ka neih manpha pen na hi;
Koi pan ka piang hong gen ding;
Bang ka hi hiam hong hilh ding.

Verse 2
Lam ka pial ciang, hong tai ding;
Honpa’ itna hong lak ding;
Lam hong hilh ding hong cing ding;
Hong thu hilh ding, hong phat ding.

Verse 3
Hih leitung gam simtham ah,
Hong hehnem ding dah na ah
Hong hilh hi nei leng up na
Mi in zong zo thei, sih na.

Verse 4
Nong hilh hi nopna ngah na’ng,
Lang pan’ mi mawhte thuak na’ng;
Ka neih manpha pen na hi,
A siangtho Lai Siangtho bu.

Verse 1
Mawhna’ zol zui kei in, Na zuih leh khial ding;
Khat vei zo phot le cin, A zom zawh nop ding;
Pasal! nakpi’n do in Lung gulh na mial pi;
Zeisu en gi ge in, Hong zawhpih ding hi.

Sakkik:
Hong huhna ding thu ngen in,
Tha hong pia hong kem ding hi;
Hong huh nuam hi Topa in;
A hong zawh pih ding hi.

Verse 2
Kholh pih gilo peel in, Kam hoih lo zang ke’n;
Pasian’ min zahtak in, A mawkna’n zang ke’n;
Thu khual in, ci tak in Thuman in migi;
Zeisu en gi ge in, Hong zawhpih ding hi.

Verse 3
A zote Pasian in Kham lu khu pia ding;
I puk kha zel hang in Up na tawh zo ding;
Eite hong Honpa in Tha hong guan’ ding hi;
Zeisu en gi ge in, Hong zawhpih ding hi.

Verse 1
Phat ding in kong pai hi Na Biak inn siang ah
Hehpih hong pia Topa Na kiang hong kha in;
Na tokhom kiang tung ding Ka ki lawm kei hi
Kong biak na thupha hang Na min thang ta hen.

Verse 2
Ki liat sak na lungsim, Ki phasak lo in;
Na minthang pahtawi ding Nang kiang ah kong pai
Khazih lungsim pha leh Lungnem na tak tawh
Na minthan na muang in Na min kong phat hi.

Verse 3
Kha Siangtho hong ompih Naang in kong thuum hi;
Ka kisap na khempeuh Na kiang ah kong ap
Kong biak nate sang in, Na minthan’ na ding;
Na thupha ka theih na’ng, Lungsim hong guan in.

Verse 4
Phat ding in kong pai Na biak inn siang ah
Hehpih hong pia Topa Na kiang hong kha in;
Kong thuciam na khempeuh A thak in bawl in;
Nasep lian sep na ding Ko te hong sawl in.

Na khuavak leh Na thuman hong zui sak in;
Na mual siangtho ah hong pai pih sak in.
Na khuavak leh Na thuman hong zui sak in;
Na mual siangtho ah hong pai pih sak in.
Aw hong zui sak in, Aw hong zui sak in;
Na mual siangtho ah hong pai pih sak in.
Amen.

Verse 1
Nang’ deih bang, Topa, Nang deih bangbang;
Nangmah belsek pa, Kei tungman bang.
Nangma deih bang in, Kei hong bawl in;
Taang lo, mang ding in, Nang kong ngak hi.

Verse 2
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang deih bangbang;
Tuni in Topa, Hong sit in Nang.
Vuk sang ngo zaw in, Tu’n hong sawp in;
Lungsim nem tak in, Nang’ mai kong kun.

Verse 3
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang deih bangbang;
Ka liam ka gim na, Hong huh in Nang,
Vangliat na khempeuh Nangma’n Na nei;
Hong dam sak in kei, Hong Honpa aw.

Verse 4
Nang’ deih bang Topa, Nang deih bangbang;
Keimah nuntak na, Hong uk in, Nang.
Khazih keima sung, Mi’n muh na ding
Hong guan’ in, kei sung Na Kha Siangtho.

Verse 1
Nun’ takna khomun kei Hong pia’n, Topa,
Galile tui li gei Na hih bang mah,
Ka lungsim vah zo kei Lai sim na tawh;
Nang mah tak ka lung deih, Hin’ na Thu aw.

Verse 2
Thuman thutak hong pia’n, Ka Topa aw,
Khomun Na piak bang zia Na thupha tawh,
Tua hi leh kol teeng kia’n Ka suak ta ding;
Thuman in hong khah khia’n Ka lung nuam ding.

Verse 3
Kei aa ding Topa Nang Nun’ tak khomun;
Kei mah ka suah tak na’ng Nangma Thu gun;
Nang tawh vantung luah na’ng Nong vaak ding hi;
Hong it sak in thuman, Itna Na hi.

Verse 4
Topa aw, Kha Siangtho Kei hong puak in,
Keima mit khua mu lo Vaaksak ding in;
Na thu thuk Lai Siangtho Hong tel sak ding,
Na Thu sung pan Nang, ko Hong mu sak ding.

Verse 1
Thumaan Lamhilh Kha Siangtho,
Tapidaw te nusia lo;
Vantung gam zuan zin mite,
A khut tawh hong len gi ge;
A gim te tawntung pha tuam,
A zak ciang Ama aw nuam;
“Vantung innpi lam zong mi,
Hong zui in, Kong kha ding hi.”

Verse 2
Hong ompih den Lawm pha pen,
Ko guak hong zawt tawm sak ke’n;
Khuamial lungman’ lau na sung’,
Nang mah’n hong ompih tawntung;
Huihpi nasia mahmah in,
Lungkia laitak hong ci in;
“Vantung innpi a zuan mi,
Hong zui in, Kong kha ding hi.”

Verse 3
Nasep na hun bei ta a,
Vantung tun’ ding bek om ta;
Kei min zong a om buang tam,
Zeisu si bek ka paulam;
Sihna gun ka ngah laitak,
Hong ci lai, siangtak, teltak;
“Vantung innpi a zuan mi,
Hong zui in, Kong kha ding hi.”

Verse 1
Topa tawh kibang zaw nuam lai ing,
A ki niam khiat bang, a mi git luat bang;
A tha nop bang, a thu maan mah bang in
Hong vai khak mah bang in, kipia’n sem nuam ing.

Sakkik:
Ka lung sung ah Nang aa bek hi nuam ing;
Ka lutang la in la, Nang aa suak hen;
Ka mawh teng sil sak in, Topa tu in
Sil siang in Nang aa ding hong keem den in.

Verse 2
Topa bang nisim thu ngen nuam ing;
Thahat nuam lai ing, singlamteh pua ding;
Hanciam nuam lai ing. Ama gam aa ding in;
Kha Siangtho sam lai, a vakthap te aa ding.

Verse 3
Topa bang in nung ta’n khang nuam ing;
Amah bang midang itna lak nuam ing;
Galile ah pumpi deih a nial bang,
Topa tawh a tawntung in kibang nuam ing.
